{{short description|Syrian historian}} '''Umar Rida Kahhalah''' (1905 - 1987) was a [[historian]], scholar, and writer from [[Damascus, Syria]]. He published many important works on [[Arab history|Arabic history]], as well as indices of biographies of [[Arab scholars]] and intellectuals.
